# Edge Recycle Classifier

## Overview
Lightweight image classifier for recyclable items, converted to TFLite and tested on Raspberry Pi.

## Files
- src/train.py - training script
- src/convert_tflite.py - conversion & quantization
- src/tflite_infer.py - inference on edge device
- models/ - saved models and tflite files
- notebooks/ - Jupyter notebooks for EDA & training

## Quick start (Colab)
1. Upload dataset to `data/` arranged by class.
2. Run `train.py` or open `notebooks/train.ipynb`.
3. Convert: `python src/convert_tflite.py`
4. Deploy `models/recycle_model_quant.tflite` and `src/tflite_infer.py` to Raspberry Pi.

## Dependencies
tensorflow, tflite-runtime, pillow, numpy, scikit-learn
